name Corn Salad with Meatballs
serves 4
tags main, salad, meat

- 680 g canned corn, drained
- 400 g kidney beans, drained
- 2 "red chillies"
- "ketchup"
- "Tabasco"
- "mango chutney"
Slice the chillies into rings. Mix the corn, beans and chillies with the ketchup, Tabasco
and mango chutney. Cover and set aside.
-> salad

- 2 avocados
- 1 lime
Halve, stone and peel the avocados and cut into slices. Juice the lime and drizzle over
the avocado. Cover and set aside.
-> avocado

- 400 g minced beef
- 3 tbsp breadcrumbs
- 0.5 tsp salt
- 1 egg
- cumin
- "onion powder"
- "garlic powder"
- oregano
- "ground paprika"
- "chilli powder"
- pepper
Mix all ingredients well and knead briefly. Shape into walnut-sized balls.

- oil
Heat in a pan and fry the meatballs for about 5 minutes. Drain on kitchen paper.
-> meatballs

- parsley
= salad
= avocado
@ meatballs
Mix the meatballs hot into the salad, add the avocado slices and garnish with parsley.
